text: Woke up today with a good feeling! I’ve had nothing to do but lay in bed since my arm so I’ve been in Twitter a lot. Your support on this album means everything to me. Gifting albums to other fans, constant online support, professional like marketing plans etc etc THANK YOU!
name: Louis Tomlinson

text:
Well that was fun! Enjoyed listening along with you all. Thanks for having me @Tim_Burgess 

Massive thank you to you the fans for your incredible support on this record. I loved every minute of making it and can’t wait for tour next year.
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: That’s the way love goes, also one of my favourites. Always loved dry your eyes by the streets and wanted to write a similar concept. Again love the strings at the end! @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Holding on to heartache is a song I’ve always loved. I’m glad I found a place for it on the deluxe. The middle 8 takes it to another gear as well! That’s going to be a fucker to sing night after night haha! @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Excited to sing this chorus on tour. Love the concept quite an English way of dealing with shit, let’s have a good night tonight and worry about it all in the morning
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Common people is about Doncaster having a place on my album. Such a big part of who I am. Love the simplicity of the song and the lyric. @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: **written in the toilet mirror
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: So we started with that title and built around. Makes the album more dynamic. Excited to hear how we do this live. @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Written in the same few days as the last two songs. Dave turned up with this picture on his phone of the title ‘She is beauty we are world class’ it was taken in the toilet mirror of a train. Felt like a weird place for such a poetic sentiment
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Can picture at the end of the night all of smashed screaming that chorus! Great memories
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Had such a great few days written with Dave Sneddon, Theo Hutchcraft and Joe Cross. Silver tongues is defo one of my favourite on the album. Love everything about this song! @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Also the strings sounds fucking lovely on this song
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: When the bass comes on the 2nd pre gets me every time
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Joe cross absolutely smashed the production, love the way the song grows. @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Saturdays. It felt emotional writing recording and performing this song. There’s something about it. Love the trainers lyric as well! @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Love the 2nd verse lyric!
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Headline I think was the last song for the album. Red triangle lads smashed the production and the academic for writing it. Made some subtle changes but loved the song as is. Don’t really have another song that feels like this on the album @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Really excited to do this live again!
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Out of my system was such a moment in the studio. I was with Nico and Dave was on zoom. I wanted to write something that had a bit of danger to it and had the title. Nico straight away played the riff and we were off! @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Doing alright at this one hand tweeting!
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: I’ve always loved All This Time. Just feel like a feel good tune from the off. James had a great vision for this song, it also helps ‘she is beauty’ not sick out on its own @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Chicago again was written in La with Dave. Love the lyric and the concept. @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Me and Dave Gibson wrote face the music together in LA. One of my favourites on the album! Love that opening lyric. Did so many great sessions with Dave!! @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: This song started of with this like hypnotic guitar riff Jay Moon came up with and we built the song around that. Feels like a good driving song. #luckyagain @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Bigger than me was a really important for me making the record. It gave me confidence early on in the process. Ambition chorus vocally but suits a big show and us singing it together @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Love the guitar line that comes in towards the end. Rob Harvey working his magic @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Written all over your face already feels like a fan favourite. Only performed it once before smashing my arm to pieces but defo really fun to do live! @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: The greatest was written in London with Fred Ball, J Moon and James Vincent McMorrow. It was always written as a tour opener but also made sense to start the album off with a bang. #TimsTwitterListeningParty @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Here we goooooo @LlSTENlNG_PARTY
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: **hear. Blame the drugs
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Glad you got to here high in California. Always loved how that song sounds
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Looking forward to this!
name: Tim's Listening Party

text:
My three favourite songs that aren’t singles, not in order and I’m sure they will change,

Face the music 
Saturdays
Written all over your face
name: Louis Tomlinson

text:
Hope everyone is doing alright! Surgery went well so hopefully slowly but surely I’m on the mend. 

I am absolutely mind blown we have a shot at number 1 in the UK. Thank you for everything! Let’s give this everything we’ve got!!
name: Louis Tomlinson

text: Vivemos dias de muita pressa e imediatismo.🚨 NAO LEIA SOMENTE A CHAMADA DA NOTICIA. Ela provavelmente foi tirada de um contexto. Pra fazer uma analise criteriosa é preciso tempo. Leia toda a reportagem, procure outras fontes confiáveis do mesmo assunto pra ter uma opinião.
name: Kaka

text: Viu uma noticia importante? Leia em 2 ou 3 veículos diferentes, veja o que é fato, é o que é opinião. Leve sempre em consideração que quem conta um conto aumenta um ponto.
name: Kaka

text: 🚨 Na busca por informações do seu candidato, tome muito cuidado na diferença entre fato e opinião. Muitos meios de comunicação, para informarem um fato, insere uma opinião, ou do jornalista ou do meio de comunicação. Problema? Nenhum! Desde que saibamos separar o fato da opinião
name: Kaka

text: Muito bom ver diferentes perspectivas, visões, realidades. Obrigado por compartilhar a opinião e experiencia de voces!! Muitas vezes não temos essa dimensão de como as coisas acontecem. E especifico na politica, como fazemos as nossas escolhas.
name: Kaka

text: Não, não se preocupe que esse conteúdo não é para empurrar um candidato. E sim pra tentarmos fazer uma escolha consciente. Como voces escolhem o candidato pra votar?

name: netflixbrasil

text:
Além do tronco Tupi, temos o Macro-Jê, e famílias linguísticas como Aruak, Karib, Pano, Tukano, Charrua, Katukina, Yanomami, Naduhup, Nambikwara, Guaikuru, Kwazá, Mura, Tikuna, Máku, Arawá, Aikaná, Txapakúra, línguas isoladas e de sinais.

#CidadeInvisivel #HistoriasVisiveis
name: netflixbrasil

text:
Hoje temos + de 274 línguas indígenas sendo faladas no país, sendo o tronco linguístico Tupi um dos mais conhecidos, porém ele não é o único. Segue o fio pra conhecer mais! 

#CidadeInvisivel #HistoriasVisiveis
name: netflixbrasil

text:
E os indígenas não estão só nas aldeias, estão também nas cidades, estamos de norte a sul do país! E isso não interfere ou anula nosso pertencimento étnico ancestral. E você, quantos povos indígenas conhece? 

/Adm: @Karibuxi 
#CidadeInvisivel #HistoriasVisiveis
name: netflixbrasil

text:
Infelizmente é muito comum associarem indígenas somente àquela pessoa de cabelo liso e olhos puxados, mas também existem indígenas de olhos redondos, cabelos cacheados, crespos, coloridos e com tom de pele do mais claro ao mais escuro.

#CidadeInvisivel #HistoriasVisiveis
name: netflixbrasil

text:
Atualmente existem mais de 305 povos indígenas no Brasil, somos diversos não só em aspectos culturais, língua e cosmovisões, mas também em nossa aparência e traços físicos! Sabiam disso?

#CidadeInvisivel #HistoriasVisiveis
name: netflixbrasil

text:
